node.text:
Follow 👉🏾@livinrentfree to learn how to buy your first 2-4 unit multifamily property. 

They told you to put it in your business name but they didn’t teach you that your cash on cash return (CoC), your return on investment (ROI) and your leverage potential was drastically underutilized with this strategy. Plus your interest rates are higher!! 

But it sounds sexy AF. 🤦🏾‍♂️🤡

FHA is the Federal Housing Administration, a government backed loan program that allows you to buy a 2-4 unit multifamily property with only 3.5% down!! As long as you live in the property for 12 months as an owner occupant, then you can move on and move out and turn it to a full blown rental that pays you EVERY month. 

Be safe out there y’all. 

Follow 👉🏾@livinrentfree to learn how to buy your first 2-4 unit multifamily property.
